{"tid":558951,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"內向嘅人/毒撚真係唔好玩交友App","createTime":"2018-02-12T17:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T02:56:15.000Z","uid":30259,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6dedea7ba7f6fd258cfa6c75801c713bc84c222c","tid":558951,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T17:15:34.000Z","msg":"內向人多數沒自信，玩交友App會好自虐，明明想識朋友但又唔敢主動，講嘢前思前顧後，變成乜都唔太敢講好拘謹。就算你真係肯主動但淨係識得講埋啲「今日天氣好好」，「食咗飯未」，「飲多啲水」嘅泛濫乏味話題，人哋都無意思同你繼續傾落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有一樣最搞笑嘅嘢係毒撚見到啲同類/醜人，都會嫌人樣衰，唔肯接受現實識番同類人，但見到靚人/活躍好動人又覺得互相格格不入高攀唔起人唔敢識人！所以內向毒撚真係唔好玩交友App"},{"pid":"632fff5b147cde880da7f5ddde6a223ae8ddcabb","tid":558951,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T17:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6f9be42ecf01bf356d3ea8f84a065982c48ddd","tid":558951,"uid":166689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T17:19:48.000Z","msg":"約完出黎就唔敢再搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚佢覺得煩"},{"pid":"49030296ed7ad3984fb84c957df1146e88907504","tid":558951,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee6f9be42ecf01bf356d3ea8f84a065982c48ddd","tid":558951,"uid":166689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T17:19:48.000Z","msg":"約完出黎就唔敢再搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚佢覺得煩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T17:21:41.000Z","msg":"毒撚根本唔識keep人，玩交友app意義何在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8e2e5c9f373c57ba9f8d2a14781191ade06dec","tid":558951,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T17:25:53.000Z","msg":"比你識到人又點，你都唔識keep人到最後都係打回原型"},{"pid":"51e8d8f6dd0064b95cd44b39e5e179572f30659e","tid":558951,"uid":73909,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid"